Preconditions:
- The input grid must not be null.
- The input grid must have at least one row and one column.
- The value of k must be non-negative.

Postconditions:
- The output grid must have the same dimensions as the input grid.
- The elements in the output grid must be shifted k times according to the given shift operation.
- The elements in the output grid must be integers within the range -1000 to 1000.